Module JavaDataStructures
Package JavaDS.Trees

Interface ITree<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - Type of data elements being sorted.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BinarySearchTree, BinaryTree, SuperTree
    public interface ITree<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>
    Interface for all one dimensional tree based data structures. Implementing classes can populate trees with Comparable extending data elements.
    Author:
    Tom Esser
